worked	out   to  help	 the  rickshaw	pliers	of  Amritsar
Municipality to become owners of cycle rickshaws. [374 A-B]
     2. The  Delhi Administration will effectively publicize
and notify  applications for  licences for  plying of  cycle
rickshaws and  all those  who apply  will be  considered  on
their merits  including length	of service as cycle rickshaw
pliers. The  criteria that  the	 Delhi	Administration	will
